http://i41.tinypic.com/2nlgyme.jpg[/img]
http://i40.tinypic.com/72pqir.jpg[/img]
[/quote]

Considering the majority of your work has text that is nondescript. And the wide range of styles used in each one. And the advanced level of animation in a couple. I’m very sure none of these are yours. Except maybe the Dibiase one.

For the xFresh Soldierx signature, I’m pretty sure that guy made the signature himself. Because I google searched his name and found a bunch of signatures he made.

http://s734.photobucket.com/albums/ww341/xFrEsH_SoLDiERx/?start=0

Plagiarism is a crime, and if you’re plagiarizing, you’re committing a crime. Not only have you lied to us before, but you’re outright stealing now. I hope they ban you permanently.

EDIT: ROFL I checked every hosting location on the images you posted, and the only two that were not tinypic are the ones with Dibiase on them. Good fucking job loser. I know you didn’t make those signatures. You fail.[/quote]

You win
